{
  "id": "campaign_guides/lure_of_the_valley/1_missions/1_15",
  "lookup_group": "campaign_guides/lure_of_the_valley",
  "lookup_id": "1.15",
  "title": "1.15",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The tagged reclaimer scuttles away, leaving a distinctive aroma in its\nwake. For the first half a kilometer, you don\u2019t even need Gus to tell\nyou where to go, but as the reclaimer gets farther and farther ahead,\nyou find yourself relying on your tiny friend\u2019s very sensitive nose."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Soon you notice the light dimming through the trees. The reclaimer\nisn\u2019t showing any signs of stopping, so you\u2019re going to have to press\non into the night if you want to stay on its trail."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "rangers-choose",
            "url": "#rangers-choose"
          }
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "rangers-choose"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A) Let the reclaimer go."
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Return"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "FIND THE NEST"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "to the mission area in the surroundings."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "B) Follow the reclaimer (ends the day)."
        }
      ],
      "color": "red"
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You spend hours traveling across the Valley with only the light\nof the moon and your lambance rigs to guide you. All the while, the yipping of Gus the mole spurs you onward."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The trail leads to a bluff overlooking the mysterious ruins\nknown as the Rings of the Moon and the Silverfin River beyond.\nThe Sentinel Star alights above the mountains, and by its cold\nradiance you see the reclaimer far below, clearly headed toward\nthe Alluvial Ruins. What better place for reclaimers to nest\nthan in the collection of ruins and detritus left by the flood that\ndestroyed the Estian arcology?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Complete"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "FIND THE NEST"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and gain the"
        },
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "INTO THE NEST"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "mission."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "strong",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "End the day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You are considered to have camped. Record your\nending location as \"The Rings of the Moon\" and your path\nterrain as \"Ravine.\""
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
